               R$ {monthlyRevenue.toLocaleString('pt-BR', { notation: "compact", maximumFractionDigits: 1 })}
             </h2>
          </div>

          <div className="flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-3 md:p-4 bg-white/5 rounded-2xl border border-white/10">
